{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Support democratic elections in Nigeria and sanction anyone who threatens them",
        "additional_details": "Recent electoral concerns have raised questions among members of the Nigerian diaspora and the international community regarding transparency and impartiality in Nigeria\u2019s democratic processes.\r\n \r\nWe call on the UK Government to use its diplomatic influence to support credible, free, and fair elections in Nigeria.\r\nWe further urge the UK Government to implement visa ban for those whose action are responsible for weakening Nigeria\u2019s opposition and or the credibility of Nigeria\u2019s election.",
        "background": "\u2022 Publicly advocate for free, fair, and transparent elections in Nigeria\r\n\u2022 Review diplomatic engagement with Nigerian electoral bodies where concerns of partisanship and impartiality arise\r\n\u2022 Implement targeted visa bans and sanctions on individuals found to be responsible for electoral malpractice",
